From cc37e22698bf40487668566cf9bab74c3790f949 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Damien Thenot <damien.thenot@vates.tech>
Date: Wed, 25 Jun 2025 17:00:22 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] feat(qcow2): Add qcow2helper

This add a C program to obtain informations about a QCOW2 that are needed.
It's used to compute allocated blocks and get bitmap.
It's better than doing this in python for performance and memory usage for
big images.
It's also using OpenMP for multi-threading accesses to the QCOW2 L2 tables.
This commit also contains what's needed in qcow2util to use this helper.

Signed-off-by: Damien Thenot <damien.thenot@vates.tech>
---
 Makefile             |   2 +
 drivers/qcow2util.py |  64 +++++-----
 qcow2/Makefile       |  24 ++++
 qcow2/qcow2_helper.c | 272 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 qcow2/qcow_helper.h  |  49 ++++++++
 5 files changed, 384 insertions(+), 27 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 qcow2/Makefile
 create mode 100644 qcow2/qcow2_helper.c
